what is synchronization in selenium?

The Automation test script speed is very high compared to web application speed

To make proper Automation script the speed of web application and automation
test script should perfectly match this process is called Synchronization.

If Synchronization is not proper than we will get "No Such Element Exception

The coordination process between the components is termed Synchronisation.

The co-ordination and speed of  the test script and the web application is matches is called synchronization.

To get the perfect synchronization we should  use implict waits  or Thread.sleep .